'''Industry Technology Facilitator''' (ITF) is an [[oil industry]] [[trade organisation]] established in 1999. It is owned by 30 major global [[oil major]]s and oilfield service companies. <ref>http://www.oil-itf.com/index/about</ref>
The group has offices in [[Aberdeen|Aberdeen, UK]], [[Houston, Texas|Houston, USA]], [[Abu Dhabi]], [[United Arab Emirates|UAE]], [[Perth]], [[Australia]] and [[Kuala Lumpur]], [[Malaysia]].<ref>http://www.oil-itf.com/index/contact</ref>{{failed verification|date=August 2014}}
